How to use file to show how to implement pagination utils in the code

Step 1: Create object of ListPaginationUtils class & pass recycler view & arraylist into it
Step 2: Implement ListPaginationListener after object creation.
Step 3: Add your API call in ListPaginationListener's overridden method onDataLoading()
        followed by index we are getting in the method.
Step 4: use startPaginationLoading() for the first time to initiate first API call.
Step 5: on API Response use
        if (mListPaginationUtils.getCurrentPageIndex() == PAGINATION_DEFAULT_INDEX) {
            //Clear your list for the first index
        }

        mListPaginationUtils.setTotalDataCount(total data count we can get from API response)
        mListPaginationUtils.completeAPICall()

        //Add all data in list
        //notify the adapter


Step 6: to reset complete API call use
        resetPaginationLoading()
        startPaginationLoading()
Step 7: use errorOccurred() wherever your API fails


